567
00:51:17,270 --> 00:51:18,200
How did you manage to do that?

568
00:51:20,870 --> 00:51:22,770
Well, you don't have to answer if you don't want to.

569
00:51:24,700 --> 00:51:26,870
Khun Phakin just wanted to check out my body.

570
00:51:29,870 --> 00:51:34,600
Hmm, does that mean you used your body in exchange?

571
