594
00:53:38,670 --> 00:53:41,070
Normally, I don't care much about the face anyway.

595
00:53:42,870 --> 00:53:43,670
Come on.

596
00:53:43,700 --> 00:53:44,500
Come this way.

597
00:53:45,400 --> 00:54:10,330
Ah. Come here, young man.

598
00:54:10,730 --> 00:54:13,030
If you want to have a future in this industry,

599
