It’s rock hard and excitedly waiting for you.

601
00:54:26,200 --> 00:54:27,000
Come on, come on.

602
00:54:29,400 --> 00:54:31,730
If you're good with your mouth and tongue,

603
00:54:32,430 --> 00:54:34,130
