606
00:54:50,370 --> 00:54:51,170
A misunderstanding?

607
00:54:52,000 --> 00:54:52,800
Really?

608
00:54:55,170 --> 00:54:56,570
You've never done this before, right?

609
00:54:58,970 --> 00:55:00,800
Try it once and you'll love it.

610
00:55:06,430 --> 00:55:07,770
It'll open up a whole new world for you.

611
00:55:13,600 --> 00:55:16,370
So, what's it going to be? Huh?

612
00:55:17,300 --> 00:55:18,230
Are you doing it or not?

613
00:55:21,170 --> 00:55:21,970
Since you're here,

614
00:55:22,370 --> 00:55:24,270
