615
00:55:25,130 --> 00:55:26,800
Once you're done, leave quickly to wherever you want to go.

616
00:55:27,870 --> 00:55:31,000
Sigh. My balls are getting completely shriveled now.

617
00:55:33,200 --> 00:55:34,000
Why?

618
00:55:35,530 --> 00:55:37,500
Are you going to chicken out?

619
00:55:40,500 --> 00:55:43,770
These new kids are all the same.

620
00:55:45,330 --> 00:55:46,130
What's it going to be?

621
00:55:47,970 --> 00:55:48,770
Huh?

622
00:55:50,470 --> 00:55:51,430
If you don't do it,

623
