634
00:56:56,330 --> 00:56:58,500
Come on, hurry.

635
00:57:04,570 --> 00:57:05,370
Come on, quickly.

636
00:57:05,570 --> 00:57:06,370
Come here.

637
00:57:23,670 --> 00:57:24,730
I just want to say that

638
00:57:25,170 --> 00:57:27,870
