639
00:57:28,270 --> 00:57:29,870
If I pass this audition,

640
00:57:30,030 --> 00:57:31,800
I'll get to be the main lead for the first time in my life.

641
00:57:31,970 --> 00:57:34,400
If P'Kajorn still can't find work for the kids,

642
00:57:34,430 --> 00:57:37,100
