643
00:57:37,500 --> 00:57:40,070
Aren't you angry at being baited for that old man to molest you like that?

644
00:57:40,570 --> 00:57:43,070
Do you really have no feelings at all?

645
00:57:44,530 --> 00:57:46,670
When you're with me, only focus on me.

646
00:57:47,430 --> 00:57:50,100
At the December Hotel, you'll get to meet Director Arthur there.

647
00:57:50,200 --> 00:57:51,070
Who are you?

